{"tid":179271,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"Strike the blood 噬血狂襲 OVA2 第5、6話","createTime":"2017-03-30T06:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T13:19:45.000Z","uid":56206,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4a29ec33df602dd15a0a34fad174b4da5fcf0f2","tid":179271,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T06:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qJLPS4E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqJLPS4E.jpg&h=6ec2a2dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【故事簡介】 <br />\n第四真祖&mdash;&mdash;是只在傳說中存在的世界最強之吸血鬼。而這位駕馭12眷獸、散播災難的幻之吸血鬼據說在日本出現了。為了監視並抹殺這位&ldquo;第四真祖&rdquo;，政府所屬的獅子王機關決定派遣攻魔師&ldquo;劍巫&rdquo;完成任務。而不知為何，被選為監視者的竟是一位見習&ldquo;劍巫&rdquo;少女&mdash;&mdash;姬柊雪菜。 <br />\n雪菜攜帶著對真祖用最強靈槍趕赴&ldquo;弦神市&rdquo;，而和她遭遇的&ldquo;第四真祖&rdquo;曉古城的真實身份卻是&mdash;&mdash;！學園幻想戰鬥劇將在浮於海上四季如夏的人工島上上演&mdash;&mdash;！ <br />\n<br />\n【STAFF】 <br />\n原作 - 三雲岳斗 <br />\n原作插畫 - 麻喵子 <br />\n監督 - 山本秀世 <br />\n監製 - 佐野隆雄 <br />\n動畫製作 - SILVER LINK.／CONNECT <br />\n<br />\n【CAST】 <br />\n曉古城：細谷佳正 <br />\n姬柊雪菜：種田梨沙 <br />\n藍羽淺蔥：瀨戶麻沙美 <br />\n曉凪沙：日高里菜 <br />\n矢瀨基樹：綠川光 <br />\n南宮那月：金元壽子 <br />\n阿斯塔魯特：井口裕香 <br />\n煌坂紗矢華：葉山郁美 <br />\n妃崎霧葉：藤井幸代<br />\n江口結瞳：東山奈央<br />\n<br />\nPV:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nkgKoBuUdW0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnkgKoBuUdW0&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=946847c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nkgKoBuUdW0</a><br />\nOP:<a href=\"http://share.dmhy.org/topics/view/324775_131030_TV_OP_-_THE_320K.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fshare.dmhy.org%2Ftopics%2Fview%2F324775_131030_TV_OP_-_THE_320K.html&d=xB%2B%2BVT6yLqhkLUe0erjI3HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=241220fb\" target=\"_blank\">http://share.dmhy.org/topics/view/324775_131030_TV_OP_-_THE_320K.html</a> <br />\nED:<a href=\"http://share.dmhy.org/topics/view/328027_131127_TV_Strike_the_Blood_ED_-_Strike_m